---

## 2. Prompt Engineering

Creating detailed instructions improves the quality of AI responses by controlling how the Gem behaves, explains concepts, and interacts with users.

---

## 3. Knowledge Integration

Adding reference files allows the AI to provide answers based on specific learning material instead of only general knowledge.

---

## 4. Practical AI Application

This project showed how AI can be customized to solve real educational problems, support students, and improve learning efficiency.

